  id: fedora_bleeding_edge
  displayName: Bleeding Edge
  rulesText: the first card you play each turn costs 1 less and deals +50%, but may crash (do nothing). crash chance rises each turn it doesn't happen and resets when it does.
  flavorText: first to every feature. first to every bug.
  designNotes: applies discount+damage mult to first-card-of-turn; escalating crash probability with reset-on-trigger; interacts with Fedora cards flagged crash-immune and with rawhide.
